comments: Nesmith (IND) is moving alongside Gordon's (PHX) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.

Replay review of the foul called on Allen (PHX) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Nesmith (IND) establishes himself in Allen's path outside of the restricted area and absorbs the contact to the front of his body, dislodging him from his position.
Allen (PHX) makes hand on ball contact and cleanly blocks Nembhard's (IND) driving shot attempt.
Mathurin (IND) reaches in and makes contact with Allen's (PHX) arm, but the contact is marginal and he is able to make the pass.
Nembhard (IND) legally contests Durant's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
As Manthurin (IND) is drawn into the air on the pump fake, he brushes Beal's (PHX) body and marginal contact occurs prior to the play near the rim being cleanly blocked.
Nesmith (IND) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Nembhard (IND) releases away from Allen (PHX) space and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Allen (PHX) moves alongside Nembhard's (IND) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) extends his arm into Nesmith (IND) and dislodges him from his defensive position.
Booker (PHX) places a forearm against Siakam's (IND) back as he turns away from the basket during his drive and the contact is marginal.

Siakam (IND) gathers the ball in the air and comes to a jump stomp, sliding his right foot backwards and establishing his left foot as his pivot foot.  He then maintains his pivot foot as he loses his balance before making the pass.
Booker (PHX) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Mathurin's (IND) driving shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) contests the shot attempt at the basket by Toppin (IND) and incidental arm contact occurs after the release of the shot.
Nesmith (IND) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.  Booker extends his leg and creates the marginal contact with Nesmith's body.
